<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.1.3">
<l>vēlai yālilaip paḷḷivi rumpiya</l>
<l>pālai yāramu tattiṉaip paintuḻāy</l>
<l>mālai yāliyil kaṇṭuma kiḻntupōy</l>
<l>ñāla muṉṉiyaik kāṇṭunāṅ kūrilē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gone rejoicing and seeing in Āli the milk</l>
<l>Where [he] enjoyed a rest on a banyan leaf in the sea,</l>
<l>Abundant nectar, and the fresh tulasī garland,</l>
<l>We will see the one whom the world contemplates in Nānkūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
